                     <interp inst="t18000528-133-person1278" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an officer:(Produces the bags.)</p>
               <p>Walker. I believe these to be the same bags.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am as innocent as the child unborn.</p>
               <p>
